just to double check. is it possible you have the cam bolted to the
cam gear incorrectly. Aren't there 5 bolts. If you perhaps got it off
on the initial bolt together, the dots on the gears would align up,
but the cam would still be off. Long shot I know, but worth a look
before reassembly. 

